'''Unilever Nepal Limited''' ('''UNL'''); ({{lang-ne|युनिलिभर नेपाल लिमिटेड}}) formerly Nepal Lever Limited is the [[Nepal]]i subsidiary company of Anglo-Dutch FMCG company [[Unilever]]. Its products include foods,beverages, [[cleaning agent]]s and [[personal care products]]. Nepal lever is one of the largest personal care company in [[South Asia]].

